[[Category:pages to sort]][[cdo:10 nguŏk 7 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[zh-min-nan:10 goe̍h 7 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[zh-yue:十月初七]] {{Lunisolar October}} '''October 7''' is the 7th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * Emperor Keikō's 40th year ( [[November 6]] , 110 in the Julian calendar ) - Emperor [[Yamato Takeru]] receives the sword [[Kusanagi no Tsurugi|Ame-no-Murakumo-no-Tsurugi]] (later known as Kusanagi-no-Tsurugi) from {{ill|Wahime-no-mikoto|ja|倭姫命|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} at Ise Shrine. == Births ==
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1538|ja|1538|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|足利義明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Koyumi-kimitokata|ja|小弓公方|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （* {{ill|1487|ja|1487|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1674|ja|1674|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Kano Tan’yū|ja|狩野探幽|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Painter|ja|絵師|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （* {{ill|1602|ja|1602|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Hashimoto Zennai|ja|橋本左内|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 士（* {{ill|1834|ja|1834|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1859th year {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Yorimizu Saburosaburō|ja|頼三樹三郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Sonzōha|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 志士・{{ill|Yoriyama|ja|頼山陽|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の子（* {{ill|1825|ja|1825|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
