'''October 7''' is the 7th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} . 

== Events ==
* Emperor Keikō's 40th year ( [[November 6]]  , 110 in the Julian calendar ) - Emperor [[Yamato Takeru]]  receives the sword [[Kusanagi no Tsurugi|Ame-no-Murakumo-no-Tsurugi]]  (later known as Kusanagi-no-Tsurugi) from {{ill|Wahime-no-mikoto|ja|倭姫命|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  at Ise Shrine.
== Births ==
== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1538|ja|1538|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|足利義明|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Koyumi-kimitokata|ja|小弓公方|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} （* {{ill|1487|ja|1487|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
* {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1674|ja|1674|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Kano Tan’yū|ja|狩野探幽|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Painter|ja|絵師|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} （* {{ill|1602|ja|1602|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Hashimoto Zennai|ja|橋本左内|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 士（* {{ill|1834|ja|1834|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
