{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月初七|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 7일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 7''' is the 7th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
== Events == * Emperor Keikō's 40th year ( [[November 6]] , 110 in the Julian calendar ) - Emperor [[Yamato Takeru]] receives the sword [[Kusanagi no Tsurugi|Ame-no-Murakumo-no-Tsurugi]] (later known as Kusanagi-no-Tsurugi) from {{ill|Wahime-no-mikoto|ja|倭姫命|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} at Ise Shrine. == Births == == Deaths == * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 7th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1538|ja|1538|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|足利義明|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|Koyumi-kimitokata|ja|小弓公方|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} （* {{ill|1487|ja|1487|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1674|ja|1674|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Kano Tan’yū|ja|狩野探幽|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|Painter|ja|絵師|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} （* {{ill|1602|ja|1602|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Hashimoto Zennai|ja|橋本左内|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 士（* {{ill|1834|ja|1834|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1859th year {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Yorimizu Saburosaburō|ja|頼三樹三郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|Sonzōha|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 志士・{{ill|Yoriyama|ja|頼山陽|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} の子（* {{ill|1825|ja|1825|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ）
